      "span_text": "In the present study, we implemented most recent recommendations from the literature using whole-brain cluster thresholding that rigorously controls type I errors  ; this could also explain why we were not able to replicate some of the previous findings (see Additional file 1: Table S3 for prior analytic approaches in this line of research)."
